POLITICAL ASYLUM; CHINESE -- UNITED STATES; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS 
-- CHINA; DEMONSTRATIONS -- SAN FRANCISCO; STUDENTS; ARRESTS; CHINA -- REVOLTS; 
