</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
BALLOONS; ACCIDENTAL DEATHS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA061289-0011 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 69074 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 12, 1989, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
