MORNING REPORT: VIDEO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Claudia Puig, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CNN Business News will start providing a daily "European Business Report" for 
viewers on July 14. The report will be offered on the cable network's 
"Moneyline," "Business Morning" and "Business Day" programs.Claudia Puig 
</P>
