</P>
<P>
L.A. Unified: 28 
</P>
<P>
Valley*: 30 
</P>
<P>
L.A. County-wide: 22 
</P>
<P>
L.A. Archdiocese: 8 
</P>
<P>
* Valley schools accounted for 4,044 (30%) of the 14,938 students (28%) in the 
district who were not screened. 
</P>
<P>
Other Area Districts With Significant Numbers 
</P>
<P>
Newhall: 46% 
</P>
<P>
Palmdale: 39 
</P>
<P>
Sulphur Springs: 37 
</P>
<P>
Burbank: 29 
</P>
<P>
